      <title>国际货币基金组织内部监管机构批评其对巨额贷款的处理方式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/imf-s-internal-watchdog-critiques-its-handling-of-largest-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，国际货币基金组织的内部监管机构批评了该银行向阿根廷和埃及等陷入困境的借款人发放异常巨额贷款的程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/imf-s-internal-watchdog-critiques-its-handling-of-largest-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 18:54:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳格尔称欧洲央行不应将利率降至中性水平以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/ecb-shouldn-t-cut-interest-rates-below-neutral-nagel-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员约阿希姆·纳格尔表示，欧洲央行可以逐步降低借贷成本至不再限制经济活动的水平，但不应降幅过大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/ecb-shouldn-t-cut-interest-rates-below-neutral-nagel-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 17:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
